subject: Baseball
lead_paragraph: Drew Hutchison came within one out of the second complete game of his career, and Jose Bautista homered and drove in three runs as host Toronto beat the Baltimore Orioles, 5-1, on Wednesday night, snapping a four-game losing streak.
